<TITLE> Families of BDR men must contact Gate-1 </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, Mar 16 (bdnews24.com) - Families of BDR members should now contact Gate-1 adjacent to BDR cinema hall instead of Gate-4 close to Rifles Square, an official said Monday. Captain Tauhid Mahmud of the information centre near BDR Gate-4 told bdnews24.com the centre would also be shifted to the Gate-1. "The Letter Box at Gate-4, however, will not be shifted to the new venue," Tauhid said. So far 110 of 245 regsitered family members met their near ones inside the BDR headquarters, he said. Tauhid said more families could register once all of those in the current list had met their loved ones at the Peelkhana headquarters. bd
